filters: Opening Film equals 'Encounters at the End of the World'
sub_questions: Which year had 'Encounters at the End of the World' as the opening film?
What is the award-winning film for that year?
How many award-winning films are listed for that specific row?

unit_annotations.Number of Screening: count of films with mixed format text

format_notes: Number of Screening column contains mixed format text like '43 films 43 televised'
Opening Film and Award-Winning Film columns contain text values that may be comma-separated or single values
Date columns do not include year information

constraints: Opening Film must match 'Encounters at the End of the World' exactly
Award-Winning Film column may contain single film or multiple films
derived_filters: Filter rows where Opening Film = 'Encounters at the End of the World'
output_format_requirements: If Award-Winning Film contains multiple films separated by delimiters, count them appropriately
If only one film is listed, return 1
